original_title: Score: The Best Of The Decade 2000-2009
overview: SCORELAND's Best of the Decade (2000-2009) is a two-disc collection of the most popular girls of the SCORELAND website of those years, as voted by its members over a 100 day countdown in late 2009. Disc one stars, in order of voting, the top models Christy Marks, Karina Hart, Merilyn Sakova, Nicole Peters, Natalie Fiore, Anna Song, Ines Cudna and Angela White. (Bea Flora (#5) and Sharday (#8) don't appear because they only did still-photo modeling for SCORE.) Disc two stars Crystal Gunns, Janet Jade, Kelly Kay, Eva Notty, Maggie Green, Joana, Cherry Brady and Morgan Leigh. With the exception of Christy Marks, Eva Notty and Cherry Brady, none of the other 13 models have ever done XXX-sex scenes with guys, an example of their immense popularity with big-boob purists. Two bonus features are video of Angela backstage, and two videos of CJ, a British girl who only modeled three times but was extremely popular.
title: Score: The Best Of The Decade 2000-2009
